Function composition is a way in which a function is mixed with other functions. During
the composition the one function holds the reference to another function in order to
fulfill itâ€™s mission.
=> compose: works with val functions
    + the later function works first with the parameter passed and then passes the return
    value to the previous function
=> andThen: works with val function
    + the first function works first with the parameter passed and then passes the return
    value to the next function
=> passing function as arguments